#### Cleanup Strategy

All test data is tracked and cleaned up automatically:

```typescript
// Automatic cleanup after each test
afterEach(async () => {
  await cleanupRegistry.deleteAll();
  await resetStore();
});

// Manual cleanup for specific scenarios
test('should handle large dataset', async () => {
  const cleanup = new CleanupHandler();
  
  try {
    const users = await createTestUsers(1000);
    cleanup.register(() => deleteUsers(users.map(u => u.id)));
    
    // Test logic here
  } finally {
    await cleanup.executeAll();
  }
});
